title: Algal Bloom Detector
description:
Built a full-stack web application with React/TypeScript frontend and
          Flask backend, featuring ocean health monitoring dashboard with
          interactive maps and analytics. Implemented machine learning pipeline
          multivariate time series forecasting, achieving 87% accuracy in algal
          bloom detection. Deployed using Netlify and Render.

title: Recipe Rating Predictor
description:
Used the provided Food.com dataset to explore, clean, and prepare
          training data with scikit-learn and pandas. Engineered features
          including one-hot tags, ingredient flags, rating statistics,
          contributor encoding, and nutrition ratios. Trained and tuned a
          RandomForestClassifier with GridSearchCV and evaluated results on
          holdout data

title: One Piece Classifier
description: Built a PyTorch image classifier for One Piece using transfer-learned CNNs on a custom dataset, shipped as a Flask web app for real-time uploads and predictions. Implemented preprocessing and confidence scoring for accurate, fast character recognition.
